        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini. <date>Secundo anno principatus domini nostri
                                <persName>Radelgari</persName>, mense Februario, quintadecima
                        indictione</date>. Ego <persName key="#Abbots #Offersio/donatio"
                            ref="#people/193">Gontarius</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas </rs><rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries #Slave #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Curtes #Fisheries #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Oil #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/122">Sancti Modesti</orgName> declaro qui domna
                            <persName ref="#people/191"
                            key="#Offersio/donatio #Princeps #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Alchisa</persName> qui fuit <rs key="#Princeps">principissa</rs>,
                        relicta domni <persName
                            key="#Princeps #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve"
                            ref="#people/186">Sichardi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Princeps">principis</rs>, quando ad obitum suum venit, omnibus
                        rebus et substantiis suis tam mobilia quam et immobilia, <rs key="#Slave"
                            >servos et ancillas</rs>, omnia et in omnibus mihi tradidit atque dedit,
                        ut de quantos exinde post suo transitu iniudicatu reliquerit, potestatem
                        habere ego illa omnia tam pro predicti domni Sichardi quam et pro predictae
                        domne Adelchise animam <rs
                            key="#Offersio/donatio #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >dare seu iudicare</rs>, dum ipsa de hac luce decesserit, de rebus illis
                        que ipsa habuit in <rs key="#Fines">finibus</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/260"
                            key="#Fines #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Canosinis</placeName> nequaquam ab ipsa exinde iudicatum apparuit. Ideo
                        ad implendum eius dispositionem, pro omnipotentis Dei misericordia et eorum
                        domni Sichardi et domne Adelchise animam salute, optuli Deo et in <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/84">Sancti
                            Benedicti</orgName> situm in <rs key="#Castle">castro</rs><placeName
                            key="#Castle" ref="#places/109"> Casino</placeName>, ubi nunc domnus
                            <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/192">Bassacius</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> esse videtur, integram ipsam substantiam seu et
                        alia quanta que ipse prefatus donus Sichardus per <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >convenientia</rs>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbati</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/187" key="#Abbots">Authperti</persName>, predicti
                        Sancti Benedicti cenobii abbas, habuit datum, et ipse prenominatus domnus
                        Sichardus per suum <rs
                            key="#Imperial/royal_diploma #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve"
                            >preceptum</rs> domne Adelchise coniugi suae concessum habuit. Finibus
                        curtis Canosine haec sunt. In prima una <rs key="#Curtes">curte</rs> qui
                        dicitur <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Landed_possessions #Fisheries #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Oil #Furniture #Churches #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/138">Milazzanum</geogName> cum <rs key="#Churches"
                            >aecclesia</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Landed_possessions #Furniture #Churches">Sancte
                            Mariae</orgName> cum omnibus <rs key="#Furniture">ornamentis</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">pertinentiis</rs> suis in finibus Canosinis,
                            <rs key="#Curtes">curtem</rs> quae vocatur <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fisheries #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Oil #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/147">Plazanum</geogName>, <rs key="#Curtes">curtem</rs> in
                            <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fisheries #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Oil #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/148">Campi</geogName>, <rs key="#Curtes">curtem</rs> in
                            <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fisheries #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Oil #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/148">Pastena</geogName>, et <rs
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">casam</rs> unam in <placeName
                            key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Castle #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/261">Cannis</placeName> cum onmi <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">substantia</rs> sua, quae esse cernitur iuxta
                        eundem <rs key="#Castle">castellum</rs>. His supradictis locis cum casis,
                        curtis, <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>, <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables"
                            >viridariis</rs>, <rs key="#Oil">olibetis</rs>, terris cultis vel
                        incultis, omnia vero et in omnibus ab ipsas curtes perinentia, seu <rs
                            key="#Fisheries">piscatione</rs> in mari, in istis supra prefatis locis
                        quantum exinde a nominata domna Adelchisa iniudicatum fuit predictum et mihi
                        modo pertinet iudicandum, in integrum in predicto Sancti Benedicti
                        monasterio offerui, ea ratione ut amodo et semper ad partem nominati
                        monasterii Sancti Benedicti eiusque rectoribus ea quae supra diximus
                        possidere valeat absque ulla cuiuslibet homini requisitionem. Quod si
                        quislibet homo surrexerit et exinde aliquod causaverit, potestatem habeant
                        eiusdem Sancti Benedicti rectoribus in vicinia Authperti abbati fuit
                        emissum. Siquis vero temerario ausu hanc nostram cartulam infringere
                        temptaverit, perpetuo supplicio cum diabolo et angelis eius sit deputatus.
                        Hanc itaque <rs key="#Offersio/donatio">cartulam offersionis</rs> ego
                        Contarius abbas in monasterio Sancti Benedicti pro anima domni Sichardi
                        principis et Alchise coniugi eius confirmavi et feci, et te <persName
                            key="#Notary">Leonem</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarium</rs> taliter ut supra dictum est scribere rogavi.
                        Ego <persName key="#Witness">Graispertus</persName> filius
                            <persName>Prasini</persName> me subscripsi. Ego <persName
                            key="#Witness #Deacons">Vvalprandus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Deacons">diaconus</rs> me subscripsi. Ego <persName key="#Witness"
                            >Ragembaldus</persName> me subscripsi. Ego <persName key="#Witness"
                            >Radichis me sub</persName>. Ego <persName key="#Witness"
                            >Pando</persName>
                        <rs key="#Witness">testis</rs>.</ab>
                </div>
